%%{init: {'flowchart': {'compactMode': true}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor GOV as Governance Head

participant UI as Governance Closure Review UI
participant BFF as Project Closure BFF
participant ORCH@{ "type":"boundary", "alias":"Journey Orchestrator"}
participant CLS as Project Closure Service
participant NS as Notification Service
participant READDB@{ "type": "database", "alias": "EPMS schema"}
participant PRIMARYDB@{ "type": "database", "alias": "EPMS schema"}
participant KAFKA@{ "type": "queue", "alias": "Message Bus"}

GOV->>UI: Open Governance closure queue item
UI->>BFF: Load closure request
BFF->>ORCH: Get Governance review detail
ORCH->>CLS: Fetch closure review view
CLS->>READDB: Read project_closure, <br/>project_closure_checklist_response, <br/>project_closure_review
READDB-->>CLS: Closure review detail
CLS-->>ORCH: Review response
ORCH-->>BFF: Response
BFF-->>UI: Show CoE-approved closure in read-only mode

alt Governance Approves
    GOV->>UI: Approve closure
    UI->>BFF: Submit Governance approval
    BFF->>ORCH: Start final approval flow
    ORCH->>CLS: Approve closure and trigger final close
    CLS->>PRIMARYDB: Insert project_closure_review <br/>(Governance approve)
    CLS->>PRIMARYDB: Update project_closure (status = Closed)
    CLS->>PRIMARYDB: Insert project_closure_status_history
    PRIMARYDB-->>CLS: Save success
    CLS-->>ORCH: Governance approval success
    ORCH->>KAFKA: Publish ClosureFinalApproved Event
    ORCH->>NS: Notify PM and CoE Head
    ORCH-->>BFF: Success
    BFF-->>UI: Show closed state
else Governance Sends Back
    GOV->>UI: Send Back closure
    UI->>BFF: Submit send back
    BFF->>ORCH: Start Governance send back flow
    ORCH->>CLS: Return closure to PM
    CLS->>PRIMARYDB: Insert project_closure_review <br/>(Governance send back)
    CLS->>PRIMARYDB: Update project_closure (status = Sent Back)
    CLS->>PRIMARYDB: Insert project_closure_status_history
    PRIMARYDB-->>CLS: Save success
    CLS-->>ORCH: Send back success
    ORCH->>NS: Notify PM
    ORCH->>KAFKA: Publish ClosureSentBackByGovernance Event
    ORCH-->>BFF: Success
    BFF-->>UI: Show sent back state
end
